Package biolockj.module.implicit.parser.wgs

This package contains Parser BioModules that convert the WGS taxonomy reports generated by WGS classifiers (such as Kraken, MetaPhlAn, or SLIMM) into standardized OTU abundance tables.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    KrakenParser
    This BioModules parses KrakenClassifier output reports to build standard OTU abundance tables.
    MetaphlanParser
    This BioModules parses MetaphlanClassifier output reports to build standard OTU abundance tables.
    SlimmParser
    This BioModule parses SlimmClassifier output reports to build standard OTU abundance tables.
